#. module: art_craft
#: model:product.template,description_sale:art_craft.product_template_23
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Acrylic Kit:\n"
"            1) Heavy Cartridge Mix Media 300 gsm paper pack of 20 A5\n"
"            2) Heavy Cartridge Mix Media 300 gsm paper pack of 20 A4\n"
"            3) Stationerie Artists’ Canvas Board 8”x10”\n"
"            4) Stationerie Artists’ Canvas Board 10”x12”\n"
"            5) Stationerie Homemade Gloss Varnish 90ml\n"
"            6) Stationerie Medium Wooden Palette (14.5×7.5)\n"
"            7) Stationerie Professional Handmade Flat Set Of 8 Hog White\n"
"            (0 1 2 4 6 8 10 12)\n"
"            8) Stationerie 2” Hog White Wash Inch Brush\n"
"            9) Stationerie Palette Knife (Sizes May Differ)\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            ຊຸດສີອາຄຣີລິກ (Acrylic Kit):\n"
"            1) ເຈ້ຍ Heavy Cartridge Mix Media 300 gsm ຊຸດ 20 ແຜ່ນ ຂະໜາດ A5\n"
"            2) ເຈ້ຍ Heavy Cartridge Mix Media 300 gsm ຊຸດ 20 ແຜ່ນ ຂະໜາດ A4\n"
"            3) ແຜ່ນຜ້າໃບ Stationerie Artists’ Canvas Board 8”x10”\n"
"            4) ແຜ່ນຜ້າໃບ Stationerie Artists’ Canvas Board 10”x12”\n"
"            5) ນ້ຳມັນເຄືອບເງົາ Stationerie Homemade Gloss Varnish 90ml\n"
"            6) ຈານສີໄມ້ Stationerie Medium Wooden Palette (14.5×7.5)\n"
"            7) ຊຸດແປງຫົວພຽງ Stationerie Professional Handmade Flat Set Of 8 "
"Hog White\n"
"            (0 1 2 4 6 8 10 12)\n"
"            8) ແປງທາສີ Stationerie 2” Hog White Wash Inch Brush\n"
"            9) ມີດປະສົມສີ Stationerie Palette Knife (ຂະໜາດອາດແຕກຕ່າງກັນ)\n"
