#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When we buy a product from a vendor or third party within a specified time, and if we are unable to sell the same item within that time, then we sell it back to them(vendor), that is called<strong> </strong>\n"
"            <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><strong>consignment purchase</strong></font><strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">.</font></strong>"
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອພວກເຮົາຊື້ສິນຄ້າຈາກຜູ້ຈຳໜ່າຍ ຫຼື ບຸກຄົນທີສາມພາຍໃນເວລາທີ່ກຳນົດ, ແລະ ຖ້າພວກເຮົາບໍ່ສາມາດຂາຍສິນຄ້ານັ້ນ"
"ໄດ້ພາຍໃນເວລາດັ່ງກ່າວ, ຈາກນັ້ນພວກເຮົາຈະຂາຍມັນຄືນໃຫ້ພວກເຂົາ (ຜູ້ຈຳໜ່າຍ), ສິ່ງນັ້ນເອີ້ນວ່າ<strong> </"
"strong>\n"
"            <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><strong>ການຊື້ແບບຝາກຂາຍ</strong></"
"font><strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">.</font></strong>"

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.about-us
msgid ""
"Write one or two paragraphs describing your product or services. To be\n"
"                                                successful your content needs to be useful to your readers."
msgstr ""
"ຂຽນໜຶ່ງ ຫຼື ສອງວັກເພື່ອອະທິບາຍສິນຄ້າ ຫຼື ການບໍລິການຂອງທ່ານ. ເພື່ອໃຫ້\n"
"                                                ປະສົບຄວາມສຳເລັດ, ເນື້ອໃນຂອງທ່ານຕ້ອງ"
